{"tid":973650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「全球第二美」周子瑜回台啦　曬逆天長腿","createTime":"2019-01-08T10:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T05:17:48.000Z","uid":74065,"like":15,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5273ecfe4f9783ce6bbfe19d742ed3f1da4c3de6","tid":973650,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"拿下2018「全球男女最美臉蛋」排行榜第二名的周子瑜回來啦！她今早搭機從韓國返台，《蘋果》在高雄小港國際機場直擊女神一人推著行李出關，雖然戴著口罩，依然散發魅力，而白色高筒鞋搭配緊身窄管牛仔褲，更展現子瑜招牌逆天長腿，令現場民眾驚呆。<br />\n<br />\n周子瑜今午一人通關，可能經紀公司保密到家，現場並未見到大陣仗粉絲。《蘋果》問她，是準備回來過年嗎？只見她微笑點頭。是否會待到農曆年後？子瑜笑說，應該不會那麼長，目前也還沒想到要去哪？<br />\n<br />\n她通關後，接機家人馬上把行李拉過去，一家人步行到停車場。台灣今年的暖冬顯然讓久住韓國的周子瑜有點不太適應，她一走出機場大廳馬上舉起右手擋陽光，走到停車場時還發生一段有趣小插曲，周子瑜一見到家人的黑色賓士休旅，立刻拉開車門上車，但媽媽卻搬不動她的行李，《蘋果》見狀還立馬上前幫抬行李，才讓一家人開心上路。<br />\n<br />\n美國電影網站「TC Candler」日前公布「2018世界百大最美臉孔」，韓國夯團「TWICE」的台灣籍成員周子瑜，去年獲得第3名，今年再往前邁進一個名次拿下亞軍。（楊適吾、林振義／高雄報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190108/640_607cce6ec4f30e31dae1149af4ed0b51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190108%2F640_607cce6ec4f30e31dae1149af4ed0b51.jpg&h=10745813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜一人拉著行李出關。林振義攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190108/640_673feec037d5d65572bf0f00cb7bedb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190108%2F640_673feec037d5d65572bf0f00cb7bedb7.jpg&h=eba917ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出關後，家人隨即把周子瑜的行李拉過去。林振義攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190108/640_f40d662d35c78a39552f34b7d52b7289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190108%2F640_f40d662d35c78a39552f34b7d52b7289.jpg&h=5d755b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不太適應台灣的暖冬，周子瑜出大廳就舉手遮陽。林振義攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190108/640_dfd36d75ba4d8881e02786ae1f2563a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190108%2F640_dfd36d75ba4d8881e02786ae1f2563a9.jpg&h=543b2596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜上車，揮手跟媒體再見。林振義攝<br />\n<br />\n關鍵字  周子瑜 長腿 過年 韓國"},{"pid":"106824c0b0278b4311abe0562bf3af211a77e57a","tid":973650,"uid":223790,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"975535c26bf8ba0bfc1c0e48cfaccb0cbd9d6456","tid":973650,"uid":148606,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:53:58.000Z","msg":"原來台灣對腳既要求咁低？<br />\n逆天？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37991f6c3aa5113658ca04106c0a766698fda1ed","tid":973650,"uid":223790,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:55:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abd93182b40cec8168570ef4109b84a3ad883729","tid":973650,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"975535c26bf8ba0bfc1c0e48cfaccb0cbd9d6456","tid":973650,"uid":148606,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:53:58.000Z","msg":"原來台灣對腳既要求咁低？<br />\n逆天？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:12:43.000Z","msg":"周子瑜 是目前全台灣最出名既女人<br />\n隨時多人識過蔡英文<br />\n<br />\n吹捧一下, 有乜問題??"},{"pid":"00999735438e27713e7d942327fe13b916663ac9","tid":973650,"uid":1977,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"著住條長褲曬乜鳩"},{"pid":"616bc6f3faf11366e03ac5ffa6c3b46ffb093cc1","tid":973650,"uid":65530,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d9745692e336cf592bb8069e6b073ce3c6e269d","tid":973650,"uid":11444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:37:53.000Z","msg":"有幾逆天呀？"},{"pid":"8c9b20d2b23a775db05e1d5bd17003cce08ca06b","tid":973650,"uid":188,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"人地叫周支瑜 尊重下人地中國人好沒？"},{"pid":"f4eaedef0723d8e330508e9777a5842b7285cc97","tid":973650,"uid":124899,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"37991f6c3aa5113658ca04106c0a766698fda1ed","tid":973650,"uid":223790,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:55:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"6、《三國演義》第七十回：&ldquo;此天賜奇功，不取是逆天也。&rdquo; [1]"},{"pid":"5ad65309344f68ca8818f2bd0f85e8d8ace9b1a6","tid":973650,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"我屌撚死支瑜!"},{"pid":"456083db7737c95fb86685dbed8506b4bc18593a","tid":973650,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f4c6d70ff72ef68d1d48fe088ee46e0cf59c372","tid":973650,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"係幾正既"},{"pid":"18bfbe92135cd95b37399d9e96d07602e757edd9","tid":973650,"uid":89660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:00:09.000Z","msg":"終於有假放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1624815acb2556b076a759a1d282847b981a35","tid":973650,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:22:32.000Z","msg":"正撚到"},{"pid":"d851ad2655be9712c3096207ea48dcc74144eff9","tid":973650,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5a1624815acb2556b076a759a1d282847b981a35","tid":973650,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:22:32.000Z","msg":"正撚到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"bfabe19c3fab12a5c3523933df2e564018b4b436","tid":973650,"uid":55519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"逆天象腿"},{"pid":"b80bdc88973275b3e89f3a3a081e667d0481a080","tid":973650,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"reply